race.comment: GREYSYND SAMMY (1) is having his first look at this course. In the placings last time (39.60) at Geelong after jumping from this draw. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Must come into calculations. ASCEND GERANIUM (6) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (42.59) at Sandown. Returns to a course where he has performed well. One of the better hopes. NEW HEIGHTS (3) ran a good time (43.46) when placing three back at The Meadows but has missed the frame since, last time out finishing fourth (34.72) at Sandown. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. LAMIA TAYA (8) deserves plenty of thought at her first run at this circuit.
